                      a.special(href='#') What is Street Work Out?
          // Two
          section#two.wrapper.alt.spotlight.style2
              .inner
                  a.image(href='#')
                      img(src='images/pic02.jpg', alt='')
                  | 									
                  .content
                      h2.major Studying 										
                      p  
                      | "Stay true to yourself now". This is the attitude I always have in my life	
                      br 
                      | I am a student now and I will be working as a programmer over time
                      br
                      | So what I can do now is to study hard, but I have a lot to do
                      br
                      | So, I usually do a lot of study and when I have time, I do other activities.				
                      a.special(href='#') What I'm Studying
          // Three
          section#three.wrapper.spotlight.style3
              .inner
                  a.image(href='#')
                      img(src='images/pic03.jpg', alt='')
                  | 									
                  .content(style='text-align: left')
                      h2.major Dancing
                      |  I like dance. among them mainly interested in street dance
                      br
                      | It's fun, but not hard, because it makes me moved while listening to the song
                      br
                      | The current main genre is bboy and I'm interested in krump, recently learning poppin
                      br
                      | I sometimes do K-pop when we can afford it, but only BTS's
                      | 										
                      a.special(href='#') what dance I'm interested in.
          // Four
          section#four.wrapper.alt.style1
              .inner
                  h2.major Where I'm affiliated
                  | 									
                  p
                  | 									
                  section.features
                      article
                          a.image(href='#')
                           img(src='images/inha.jpg', alt='')
                          h3.major(style='text-transform: none') Inha Univ, Comp.Sci 											
                          | 										
                          a.special(href='#') Learn more
                      | 										
                      article
                          a.image(href='#')
                            img(src='images/neters.jpg', alt='')
